<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's becoming quite the rising presence on social media, having amassed almost 150,000 followers – and counting – on her Instagram account.</p>

<p>And Sophia Peschisolido treated her followers to yet another delightful fashion post earlier this week, when she shared snaps of herself in a flattering white minidress.</p>

<p>The 23-year-old daughter of The Apprentice star Karren Brady, 51, posed up a storm in the summery number, which she teamed with a matching wide-brimmed hat.</p>

<p>Delightful: Sophia Peschisolido treated her followers to yet another delightful fashion post earlier this week, when she shared snaps of herself in a flattering white minidress</p>

<p>With her blonde locks styled in a straight sleek blowout, the model highlighted her good looks with an impeccably-applied palette of makeup.</p>

<p>Teaming her PrettyLittleThing ensemble with a Louis Vuitton purse and a pair of white Nike Air Force 1 trainers, the brunette beauty posed up a storm.</p>

<p>Captioning the pair of scintillating snaps, Sophia wrote: 'Sunshine makes me happy.' </p>

<p>Strike a pose: The 23-year-old daughter of The Apprentice star Karren Brady, 51, posed up a storm in the summery number, which she teamed with a matching wide-brimmed hat</p>

